{"tid":1785549,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"反共的功夫佬 - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2019-12-16T12:45:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-16T12:58:43.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"31486df3bbc3eed9fcdc7cd3ca7fc69b8a4473a8","tid":1785549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:45:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191216/20825682/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825682%2F&d=dVEf9brN%2BTtwApumOSMW7rAecByD1k%2Bs4QbbWwjAUoc%3D&h=cf490e20\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25A6%25AE%25E7%259D%258E%25E4%25B9%25BE%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20191216%2F20825682%2F&h=71407525\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%A6%AE%E7%9D%8E%E4%B9%BE/daily/article/20191216/20825682/</a><br />\n<br />\n反共的功夫佬 - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20191216/large/1576396451_5c50.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20191216%2Flarge%2F1576396451_5c50.jpg&h=5e0c4a7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《一拳超人》圖片(互聯網)<br />\n<br />\n昨天寫「藍色暗星圈」，提及一個叫李嘉的人，記性甚佳的讀者陳君告訴我，幾年前李嘉在Facebook上，曾貼出我寫《一拳超人》的文章，但沒提及作者名字和文章出處。陳君覺得這樣轉載很不妥，留言提醒他補上出處，誰知李嘉馬上把留言刪除並block掉陳君。這件事跟政治無關，只跟品格有關。今天仍然撐警的人，大概就是這樣的道德水平。<br />\n<br />\n我看了陳君的留言後，好奇瀏覽一下李嘉Facebook，發現他日前寫下一段話：「不要和我談甚麼民主、人權等西方的浪漫廢話！！！老子只是一名功夫佬，匹夫也！老子的身體、靈魂、功夫全部都是地地道道中國製造，祖先留給老子的！吾盡匹夫之責全身心地愛護守護我的祖國，並堅定牢固地支持為守護祖國大地而默默付出的每一人。」<br />\n<br />\n我作為愛國深藍絲，有三點回應。一、從「功夫佬」的言行舉止，我絲毫看不出中國文化美德，只見到一種野蠻人的劣質。中國文化崇尚謙讓，講「滿招損，謙受益」、「循牆而走」，功夫佬則高傲地自稱「老子」，這是哪門子中國文化？<br />\n<br />\n二、功夫佬以「中國製造」為榮，強調「守護祖國」，好啊，請你馬上殺入中南海「光復中國」，不要在網上打嘴炮。今天中國的執政黨，指導理論是馬列主義，政治手段崇尚階級鬥爭，當年由蘇俄老大哥扶植，由頭到腳充滿外國勢力。既然「民主、人權」是西方浪漫廢話，共產主義當然也是西方浪漫廢話，你守護中國，現在可以反共了！<br />\n<br />\n三、孟子說：「是非之心，人皆有之。」你覺得示威者做錯，沒問題，但一個有是非之心的人，今天也不可能認為警察做對。要為亂局負最大責任的，肯定是政府和警察，試想一下：六月十二日警方犯了很多危害公眾的錯誤，假如林鄭月娥能馬上正視，按既有程序調查及停職犯規警員，之後的亂象完全可以避免。連是非之心也欠缺的，孟子根本不會同意你是人。<br />\n<br />\n自稱「中國人」之前，請先fact-check你是否一個人，謝謝合作。 <br />\n<br />\n馮睎乾<br />\n電郵 :philomusus@gmail.com"},{"pid":"b279072870761cde8a56abd367953c46f14b66ea","tid":1785549,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:47:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PY03AQa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPY03AQa.jpg&h=511bc04b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cMC8VCF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcMC8VCF.jpg&h=36102201&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;_nc_oc=AQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-sin2-2.xx&amp;oh=f485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a&amp;oe=5EAED219\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-sin2-2.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F79171653_153614429381900_7842117770006233088_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26_nc_oc%3DAQmucP1kby-cRITxgOACmF7RLYKzS6mhC3XxyWj80ckb-U-hZ0QLjDM4FkacBa8he0c%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-sin2-2.xx%26oh%3Df485126eda1dc3e8f819bf943c798b1a%26oe%3D5EAED219&h=70a59658&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/NTntx6h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FNTntx6h.jpg&h=228c1213&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d035f53cbfa04dca165dd231aa1ffbedf6d4c939","tid":1785549,"uid":95499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-16T12:53:25.000Z","msg":"之前連登仲有班人吹奏李嘉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有幾好打就唔係自己講嘅 要上過擂臺先知嘅"},{"pid":"b49228077f17dbfb5